<p class="v2-structure-link"><b>Message Structure:</b> <a href="StructureDefinition-MFN_M08.html">MFN_M08</a></p>
<div class="paragraph">
<p><em>MFI-1 -</em> Master <em>File Identifier</em> = OMA for numeric observations.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>A service/test/observation definition may have both an OM2 (numeric) and OM3 (categorical) segment included in case the value may be either numeric and/or categorical.</p>
</div>
